{
  "stem": "11844.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I go to my cousin, Julius [INAUDIBLE], Beethovenstraat 106.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Now, it's around 5:00, 6:00.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I come to my cousin and only his wife was there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she looks at me and she says, Eric, you're so smart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You always come shortly before dinner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, that's right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was sitting there and talking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the meantime, her husband came home, and her son.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Name of the son was Heinz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they all said to me, Eric, you are so-- so quiet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You usually talk so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What's wrong?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's something wrong.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I told them what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, that's terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Thank God nothing happened to our son and to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Minute later, a neighbor came in-- young woman-- and said, they're going into houses and take out Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Get rid of Heinz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my cousin picked up the telephone, called a non-Jewish friend, and said, can I send over my son?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're going into houses, taking out the Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "By the way, the same thing happened in the central Amsterdam in February of '41, the big situation where they also took about 400.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, my cousin called a friend, talked about Heinz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody talked about me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt very, very lonely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Heinz and I, we went down and into-- there was an elevator.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We walked down the stairs, was second or third floor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I said to Heinz, Heinz, lets divide the risk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One goes left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One goes right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Which way do you go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, well, my bicycle is on the left, so I'll go to the left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He did. 30 to 40 yards later, I heard the sque-- squeaking of some brakes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I turned around.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
